title: VALORANT New Team Deathmatch Game Mode Official Trailer
description:
A new Team Death Match mode is making its way to Valorant as part of Episode_07 // Act 1 with some new maps as well. Don't worry about Econ just get out there and slay.

Team Deathmatch is on its way, and Maxbot’s pulling the strings. Prepare for three new maps, high-octane action, and plenty of ways to flex your plays.

Artist name: overunder
Song title: The Drop (feat. Christian Foley)
